data.description: Great starter home located in Lancaster Tx, This home offers 3 bedrooms 1.5 bath, spacious familyroom and good size backyard with carport that covers up to 3 cars, Back Alley access! . The property also has Ceramic tile throughout home, New HVAC System, Enclosed patio ,its located next to a church Parking lot so no neighbor on one side !Near schools, local stores, parks and is easily accessible to major highways. Come see this home today !
